Text: Enron closes the first financial power Swap with an LDC in ArgentinaEnron and EDEN an AES Co signed the ISDA Master Agreement and immediately after executed the first financial power swap transaction with an LDC Terms Conditions Volume MWh hoursday days week Term year starting February st Fixed Price USMWh Floating Price Payer Enron North America Fixed Price Payer Eden SA Thanks Rolo
